<br>
- Savage HTH Quest Rewards are Inferior - When performing quests,<br>
Savages are finding the the HTH weapon rewards they receive are inferior to<br>
their axe counterparts.<br>
<br>
For example, let's look at two separate quests:<br>
<br>
Varulbane Quest:<br>
<br>
Varulbane Axe<br>
DPS: 15.0<br>
SPD: 3.0<br>
QUA: 100%<br>
